reviewText:
Four under-funded poorly produced vignettes. Film school C+ at best.

Boring stories about under-developed characters leaves one with a vague ennui.

Not even a glimpse of Corinne Bohrer's breasts can instill interest.

Your money is best spent elsewhere.
The first movie wad good. But the others were below par. I would not recommend this movie. It is a waste of time
